## Common Pitfalls
- Schema creates as `dv_{{ staging_schema }}` instead of `{{ staging_schema }}` -> Check `generate_schema_name` macro
- External table errors -> Run `dbt run-operation stage_external_sources` first
- Cross-database error -> Replace hardcoded DB with {% raw %}`{{ target.database }}`{% endraw %}
- Object in wrong schema -> Check folder structure matches dbt_project.yml config

## Mermaid ER Diagrams

**After every model change, update the ER diagrams!**

| Model Folder | Diagram |
|---------------|----------|
{% if include_example %}| `models/raw_vault/adworks/` | `design/raw-vault/adventureworks/vault-model.mmd` |
{% endif %}| `models/raw_vault/_common/` | `design/raw-vault/_integrated/overview.md` |

### Format
```mermaid
erDiagram
    %%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
    %% Schema: {{ schema_prefix }}_<concept>

    HUB_ENTITY {
        char64 hk_entity PK
        bigint object_id
        datetime2 dss_load_date
        varchar dss_record_source
    }

    HUB_ENTITY ||--o{ SAT_ENTITY : has
```

### Rules
- **Theme:** `base` (neutral, no bright colors)
- **File extension:** `.mmd`
- **Attributes:** `type name [PK|FK]` (no comments after PK/FK)
- **Relationships:** simple labels, no quotes
